article.headline: Columbia secures 75-56 victory against Maine
article.description: — Zine Eddine Bedri had 14 points in Columbia's 75-56 victory against Maine on Saturday.
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Zine Eddine Bedri had 14 points in Columbia's 75-56 victory against Maine on Saturday. Eddine Bedri went 5 of 10 from the field for the Lions (5-2). Geronimo Rubio De La Rosa scored 12 points and Josh Odunowo had 10. Peter Filipovity finished with 10 points and nine rebounds for the Black Bears (4-4). Kellen Tynes added 10 points, five assists and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
